text: Kirchseeon is a market town in the Upper Bavarian district of Ebersberg and is 15 km east of Munich city limits. The nearest communities are Grafing and Ebersberg. The Bavarian capital, Munich, can be reached by S-Bahn (line S4), which runs over the Munichâ€“Salzburg line.
